title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Ben Leber/Chad Graff/Lavelle Neal
description: Nordo kicks the show off with a boom getting you HYPED for the start of Vikings training camp.  Ben Leber joins the show for some Vikings conversation.  The Athletic's Chad Graff chats with Nordo about some behind the scenes info on the Vikings training camp.  Plus, Lavelle Neal calls in for some Twins talk!
